'''溫帶落葉林'''<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://terms.naer.edu.tw/detail/1077726/?index=1 |title=temperate deciduous forest - 溫帶落葉林 |access-date=2020-09-29 |archive-date=2021-02-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210213135913/http://terms.naer.edu.tw/detail/1077726/?index=1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>（{{lang-en|temperate deciduous forest}}），或稱'''溫帶闊葉林'''（{{lang-en|temperate broad-leaf forest}}），是一种分布于[[温带|温带]]（700m以下）、暖温带的森林类型。以經年性落葉[[喬木|喬木]]、[[木本植物|木本植物]]為主，分布於夏季溫暖潮濕，冬季較不嚴寒的地區，或是[[微氣候|微氣候]]較明顯的山地區域。<ref>Archibold, O. W. 1995. ''Ecology of World Vegetation,'' London: Chapman and Hall.</ref>

由於分布地的氣候與土壤性質，溫帶落葉林的林相多樣性較高，具有代表性的樹種為：[[櫟屬|橡樹]]（[[學名|學名]]：{{lang|la|''Quercus''}}）、[[楓屬|楓樹]]（學名：{{lang|la|''Acer''}}）、[[山毛櫸屬|山毛櫸]]（學名：{{lang|la|''Fagus''}}）、[[榆屬|榆樹]]（學名：{{lang|la|''Ulmus''}}）等。<ref>Keddy, P.A. 2007, ''Plants and Vegetation: Origins, Processes, Consequences,'' Cambridge University Press, Cambridge, UK.</ref>

大部分溫帶[[落葉林|落葉林]]分布地位於[[北半球|北半球]]，如[[北美|北美]]東部、[[亞洲|亞洲]]東部<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.annualreviews.org/doi/abs/10.1146/annurev.ecolsys.30.1.421 |title=Wen, J. 1999. Evolution of eastern Asian and eastern North American disjunct distributions in flowering plants. Annual Review of Ecology and Systematics 30:421-455 |accessdate=2014-03-26 |archive-date=2019-05-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190528161634/https://www.annualreviews.org/doi/abs/10.1146/annurev.ecolsys.30.1.421 |dead-url=no }}</ref>及[[歐洲|歐洲]]地區，在[[南美洲|南美洲]]南部、[[澳洲|澳洲]]也有少量分布。<ref>Archibold, O. W. 1995. Ecology of World Vegetation. London: Chapman and Hall. Figure 6.1</ref>

目前全世界最大的溫帶落葉林保護區為[[美國|美國]]的[[大煙山國家公園|大煙山國家公園]]。<ref>Braun, E. L. 1950, ''Deciduous Forests of Eastern North America,'' New York: Hafner</ref><ref>Whittaker, R. H. 1956. Vegetation of the Great Smoky Mountains. Ecological Monographs 26: 1–79.</ref>

